OL,3,CSNP promise 'Welcome to School Bag' to
OL,4,Cbuild on Baby Box
OL,6,FThe First Minister has promised to
OL,7,Fintroduce a "Welcome to School Bag" if
OL,8,Fthe SNP returns to power in May.
OL,10,FJohn Swinney said the plans would
OL,11,Fbuild on the "fantastic success" of
OL,12,Fthe Baby Box.
OL,14,FThe Welcome to School Bag would be
OL,15,Fprovided to all Primary 1 pupils in
OL,16,FScotland.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@cO]sD@NOUsD@`O]
