OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776161176
OL,3,CSNP promise 'Welcome to School Bag' to
OL,4,Cbuild on Baby Box
OL,6,FIt would contain a school bag with a
OL,7,Fstarter pack filled with "essential
OL,8,Fschool items" including stationery,
OL,9,Fbooks, a water bottle and "resources
OL,10,Fto help families encourage literacy
OL,11,Fand numeracy practice at home".
OL,13,FIt follows a similar principle to the
OL,14,FBaby Box which was introduced by
OL,15,FNicola Sturgeon in 2017.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@MO]qD@[OUsD@^O]
