OL,3,CSNP promise 'Welcome to School Bag' to
OL,4,Cbuild on Baby Box
OL,6,FEvery new mother is entitled to a box,
OL,7,Fwhich is delivered a few weeks before
OL,8,Fher due date, and includes items such
OL,9,Fas books, clothes and a digital
OL,10,Fthermometer, while the box itself can
OL,11,Fbe used as a sleeping space.
OL,13,FMr Swinney said the SNP's new plan
OL,14,Fwould ensure children are supported at
OL,15,Fevery stage of their life.
OL,17,FHe said: "I am delighted to launch our
OL,18,Ffantastic new Welcome to School Bag
OL,19,Ftoday.
OL,26,@yD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
