OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776161176
OL,3,CSNP promise 'Welcome to School Bag' to
OL,4,Cbuild on Baby Box
OL,6,F"Starting school is an exciting moment
OL,7,Ffor every child and their family and I
OL,8,Fam determined that we do everything we
OL,9,Fcan to support them at such a big
OL,10,Ftransition point in their life.
OL,12,F"The Welcome to School Bag will be
OL,13,Fpacked with items: stationery, books
OL,14,Fand other helpful resources, to help
OL,15,Four children thrive when starting
OL,16,Fschool.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
