PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776161176
OL,3,CSNP promise 'Welcome to School Bag' to
OL,4,Cbuild on Baby Box
OL,6,F"Building on the fantastic success of
OL,7,Fthe Baby Box, Scotland's Welcome to
OL,8,FSchool Bag is just another step in
OL,9,Fensuring that we are supporting our
OL,10,Fchildren at every stage of their life.
OL,12,F"The Baby Box has been
OL,13,Ftransformational for so many families
OL,14,Facross the country and receiving it is
OL,15,Fnow an important milestone for new
OL,16,Fparents. The Welcome to School Bag has
OL,17,Fthe potential to have the same impact.
OL,19,F"That is what you get with the SNP ` a
OL,20,Fgovernment that is always on
OL,21,FScotland's side."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU{D@AOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
