OL,3,CSNP promise 'Welcome to School Bag' to
OL,4,Cbuild on Baby Box
OL,6,FPaul O'Kane, Scottish Labour's
OL,7,Feducation spokesman, said the SNP had
OL,8,Fa "long list of broken promises when
OL,9,Fit comes to supporting schools and
OL,10,Fyoung people".
OL,12,FHe said: "At the 2021 election, they
OL,13,Fcommitted to giving free laptops to
OL,14,Fall school pupils in Scotland, but
OL,15,Fthis pledge has since been ditched.
OL,17,F"They promised to expand free school
OL,18,Fmeals to all primary school pupils but
OL,19,Fhave failed to deliver.
OL,26,@pD@COUrD@MO]tD@JOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776161176
OL,3,CSNP promise 'Welcome to School Bag' to
OL,4,Cbuild on Baby Box
OL,6,F"They insisted they would provide free
OL,7,Fbikes for all schoolkids who can't
OL,8,Fafford them but have fallen woefully
OL,9,Fshort on this ambition.
OL,11,F"And they vowed to eliminate the
OL,12,Fattainment gap, yet the gap between
OL,13,Fthe richest and poorest pupils in our
OL,14,Fschools is wider than it was before
OL,15,Fthe Covid pandemic.
OL,17,F"Amid their trail of broken promises,
OL,18,Fthere has been a rise in the number of
OL,19,Fkids skipping school and families
OL,20,Fcan't get the support they need."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776161176
OL,3,CSNP promise 'Welcome to School Bag' to
OL,4,Cbuild on Baby Box
OL,6,F"The SNP simply cannot be trusted.
OL,7,FThey make pledges before polling day
OL,8,Fwith no intention of delivering. The
OL,9,Fpeople of Scotland deserve better."
OL,11,FScottish Lib Dem education
OL,12,Fspokesperson Willie Rennie said: "The
OL,13,FSNP love to announce freebies at
OL,14,Felection time and then ditch them the
OL,15,Fmoment polling day has passed.
OL,17,F"Last election it was bikes and
OL,18,Ftablets, this time it's school bags.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@cO]tD@bOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
